hwMeta.bodyText:
If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        readData_vld(0),
        readDataPending(0),
        readDataOverflow_vld(0)
    ).Else(
        readData_vld(readData_vld_next),
        readDataPending(readDataPending_next),
        readDataOverflow_vld(readDataOverflow_vld_next)
    )
)

If((~readDataOverflow_vld & (~readData_vld | r_data_rd) & r_addr_vld)._eq(1),
    ram_we(0),
    ram_addr(r_addr_data)
).Else(
    ram_we(1),
    ram_addr(w_addr)
)

If(readDataPending._eq(1),
    If((~readData_vld | r_data_rd)._eq(1),
        readData_data_next(ram_dout),
        readData_vld_next(1),
        readDataOverflow_vld_next(0),
        readDataOverflow_data_next(readDataOverflow_data)
    ).Else(
        readDataOverflow_data_next(ram_dout),
        readDataOverflow_vld_next(1),
        readData_data_next(readData_data),
        readData_vld_next(readData_vld)
    )
).Elif(r_data_rd._eq(1),
    readData_data_next(readDataOverflow_data),
    readData_vld_next(readDataOverflow_vld),
    readDataOverflow_vld_next(0),
    readDataOverflow_data_next(readDataOverflow_data)
).Else(
    readDataOverflow_data_next(readDataOverflow_data),
    readDataOverflow_vld_next(readDataOverflow_vld),
    readData_data_next(readData_data),
    readData_vld_next(readData_vld)
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        write_ptr(0),
        read_ptr0(0),
        looped0(0)
    ).Else(
        write_ptr(write_ptr_next),
        read_ptr0(read_ptr0_next),
        looped0(looped0_next)
    )
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        write_ptr(0),
        read_ptr0(0),
        looped0(0)
    ).Else(
        write_ptr(write_ptr_next),
        read_ptr0(read_ptr0_next),
        looped0(looped0_next)
    )
)

If(clk._onRisingEdge(),
    If(rst_n._eq(0),
        write_ptr(0),
        read_ptr0(0),
        looped0(0)
    ).Else(
        write_ptr(write_ptr_next),
        read_ptr0(read_ptr0_next),
        looped0(looped0_next)
    )
)
